description:
Amarok 3.2 open-source music player app is now available for download with initial Qt 6 and KDE Frameworks 6 port, as well as other changes. Here's what's new!

The post Amarok 3.2 “Punkadiddle” Music Player Officially Released, Ported to Qt 6 appeared first on 9to5Linux - do not reproduce this article without permission. This RSS feed is intended for readers, not scrapers.
title: Amarok 3.2 “Punkadiddle” Music Player Officially Released, Ported to Qt 6
